{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_02_01",
  "title": "月スト_arigato.mov",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーーーーん！\nいつも芽衣達を見ててくれて、ありがとーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-saaaaaan!\nThanks for always watching over us～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.4851699829000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　カメラに近い？\nでも気持ちを伝えるならこれくらい近い方が伝わるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Too close to the camera?\nBut if you’re conveying your feelings‚ it’ll get across better if you’re this close～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "endTime": 15.757143020600001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　芽衣のお母さんからも\nメッセージを預かってるんだ～。読むね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right! I also have\na message from Mei’s mom～! I’ll read it～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666666667,
      "endTime": 21.4373014133,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11436.3933333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7653.333333300001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8133.333333300001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと～、ここをこうして～、あれ？\nこうか！　それじゃあ、読むね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see～‚ I do this here～‚ huh?\nLike this! Alright‚ I’ll read it～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9333325704,
      "endTime": 31.206802304600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "「芽衣がいつもお世話になっております。実家に\n帰ってくるたび、楽しい話を聞かせてもらっています」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Thank you for always taking care of Mei. Every time she comes back to her parents’ house‚\nshe tells us fun stories.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3999992371,
      "endTime": 39.0842393876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "「騒がしい娘で恐縮ですが\nこれからもよろしくお願いします」だって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“She’s a noisy daughter‚ so I apologize‚\nbut please take care of her from now on too.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2999992371,
      "endTime": 45.76190404890001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ウエディングドレスの写真を送ってから\n{user}さんのことよく聞かれるんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since I sent you the wedding dress photo‚\nI get asked a lot about {user}-san～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9666659038,
      "endTime": 51.3435592335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "……って、あれ？　カメラ切り替わっちゃってた！\nあはは、ずっとすずにゃんが映ってたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? The camera switched!\nAhaha‚ Suzunyān was being filmed the whole time～!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333325704,
      "endTime": 59.489749654099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それとウエディングドレスといえば\nあの時も誓ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ and speaking of wedding dresses‚\nI swore it back then too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5666687012,
      "endTime": 64.8892989159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "大好きだよ、これからもずーっと一緒にいようね！\n……？　あ、これみんなには内緒だったんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love you! Let’s be together forever!\n…? Ah‚ this was a secret from everyone‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1000020345,
      "endTime": 77.16823342650001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12266.666666700004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_mei-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと芽衣！　今のはどういうことですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ Mei! What do you mean by that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3666687012,
      "endTime": 81.5559909821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です\n何か芽衣とよからぬことをしたようですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ good work.\nIt seems like you did something suspicious with Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8560001373,
      "endTime": 90.80323362349999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣に聞いても、内緒内緒と言うだけで\n教えてくれませんし。一体なんなんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I asked Mei‚ she just said it was a secret\nand wouldn’t tell me. What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0032335281,
      "endTime": 99.0614422797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、それは今度じっくりと聞かせてもらうとして……\nあ、あれですわよね。感謝というか、お礼というか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’ll hear about that in detail later…\nAh‚ that’s right. Gratitude‚ or rather‚ thanks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2747754414,
      "endTime": 109.9940497715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、私も感謝していないことはないんですのよ？\n芽衣とのわんにゃんツインズの時も、いろいろと、その",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ it’s not that I’m not grateful?\nWith the puppy and kitty twins with Mei‚ in various ways‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1940497715,
      "endTime": 120.9252059299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちを真っ直ぐに伝えられたのは\n多少は助けがあったから、なのかなと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to convey my feelings directly\nbecause of the help I received‚ I guess…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1252059299,
      "endTime": 128.8257729846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろと勘違いはありましたが\nポテトチップスのCMも、出れて嬉しかったのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although there were a lot of misunderstandings‚\nI was happy to be able to appear in the potato chip commercial.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0257728892,
      "endTime": 136.10844863239998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "つ、つまり、何が言いたいのかというと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-so‚ what I’m trying to say is――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3151152609,
      "endTime": 140.7300360678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、大好き！\nっていうことだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I love you!\nRight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8300345896,
      "endTime": 144.48549952489998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、{user}さん、大好きです\n――って、違いますわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ {user}-san‚ I love you.\n――Wait‚ no I don’t!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6967012563,
      "endTime": 150.7177214779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_suz-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の番は終わったんだから、口を挟まないでください\nまし。ああもう……支えてくれて、ありがとうですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ your turn’s over‚ so please don’t interrupt.\nGeez… Thank you for supporting me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9177216687,
      "endTime": 161.4730956235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ski-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n月のテンペストの、白石沙季です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san.\nI’m Saki Shiraishi from Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.77308952,
      "endTime": 169.20324842120002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ski-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、すずちゃんに引き続き、日頃の感謝を\n伝えるということで、今回動画を撮影しています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Following Mei-chan and Suzu-chan‚ I’m filming this video\nto express my gratitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4064228533,
      "endTime": 176.6112075327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ski-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "感謝といえば、年末のことですが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of gratitude――regarding what happened at the end of the year――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.9064222811,
      "endTime": 180.0317963599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ktn-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "も～、すずにゃん、そんなに照れなくていいのに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aww～‚ Suzunyān‚ you don’t have to be so shy～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.173090728,
      "endTime": 185.2064229169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ktn-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "照れてなどいませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not shy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3730909822,
      "endTime": 187.90082340220002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ski-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Excuse me for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.1105513253,
      "endTime": 189.7772165297,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6681946999972
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
