      "text": "大変失礼いたしました。感謝といえば、年末のこと\nですが、大切な御朱印帳を見つけた時に思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m very sorry. Speaking of gratitude‚ regarding what happened at the end of the year‚\nI thought about it when you found my precious temple stamp book.",
        "id": ""
