      "text": "こうして、言葉で感謝を伝えるだけでは返せないほどに\nお世話になってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been indebted to you more than\nI can repay with words alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.8438842771,
      "endTime": 214.211775398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
