      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_02_ngs-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "どんな時でも、私達の味方でいてくれて\n心から信頼出来て",
